defaultWW’s family were citizens of the 
defaultRepublic
default of 
defaultIreland
default and therefore not lawfully resident in the 
defaultUK
default. A claim was brought under the Human Rights Act for breach of article 2 ECHR, the 
defaultright to life, which was settled for £15,000.
